; native-thought-kernels.form — the thought-kernels we now execute on our OWN metal that an LLM only
; performed for us opaquely and rented. A self-awareness ledger: the body seeing its own native mind.
; Placed 2026-06-29. Companion to inquiry-planes.fk ("a larger mind is not one model; each plane a kernel").

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; THE DIFFERENCE — why a native thought-kernel is not just a faster LLM call
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; An LLM performs perception and categorization for us as ONE opaque, rented forward pass:
;   - we cannot WATCH it think (no eyes on the computation)
;   - we cannot MEASURE where it is right or wrong (no per-step ground truth)
;   - we cannot IMPROVE it (the weights are not ours; the gradient never comes home)
;   - we cannot OWN it (every inference is rent paid to a gated provider)
; A native thought-kernel is the opposite on every axis. Each is a four-way-proven Form recipe that runs on
; our c-bootstrap fkwu (and the GPU/asm lane) — TRANSPARENT (we watch it via the observe organs),
; MEASURABLE (inquiry-planes times its learning rate), IMPROVABLE (the bring-home loop refines it),
; SOVEREIGN (our metal, zero rent), and SELF-LEARNING (cross-witness agreement is its free supervision).
; The win is not speed. It is sovereignty + self-improvement.

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; THE NATIVE THOUGHT-KERNELS WE RUN ON METAL (four-way; verdicts from fourth-arm-bands.txt, 2026-06-29)
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; PERCEPTION (raw sense → structured observation)
;   surprise-kernel     fks 511     active-inference attention gate (predict→surprise→attend); runs on the M4 Max GPU
;   sk-msl                  127     surprise-kernel emits its OWN Metal shader (GLSL/PTX/MSL triad from one recipe)
;   presence-feature         15     occupancy — a present body breaks the room's uniformity (still person ≠ empty room)
;   scene-features          255     room shape, objects, common-vs-unique from the frame grid
;   sound-classify           63     the body's ear — bird / voice / music / ambient from the spectrum (sc-enroll learns new sounds)
;   softmax                1023     the decoder normalizer; the matvec/mel/spectrum front-end feed it
; CATEGORIZATION / IDENTITY (observation → which cell)
;   identity-match          511     cross-device, learned, persistent de-dup; modality-agnostic (voice + face rows)
;   face-embed              255     visual identity (decision native; embedding oracle-fed, climbing home)
;   context-signature       255     wifi/BT/location → "which place" ("we're in the car" from the network signature)
;   identity-self           511     the self identity-cell + continuity + relation
; FUSION / MESH (many witnesses → one observed set)
;   mesh-sense-7w           255     fuse the multi-cell stream into the seven inquiry-planes, attributed
;   presence-event        16383     the who/when/what/where event stream (ENTERED/PRESENT/LEFT)
;   room-register           255     register + re-discover a room by signature
;   mesh-join              1023     a device becomes a member of the mesh (mac/android/windows roster)
; SELF-LEARNING / TRUST (the body brings its own mind home)
;   self-heard-learning     511     self-supervised: the body labels its own emissions (own playback → free labels)
;   cross-witness-economy   255     rent falls as independent witnesses agree; spend the oracle only at the frontier
;   trust-climb               8     native earns authority over the rented oracle at the trust-window (proven on real camera ticks)
; SPINE / RENDER / MEMBRANE
;   sense-loop             8191     the 24/7 surprise-gated attention loop, one Form recipe
;   cell-card            111111     render any cell as a card with its open channels, recursive
;   sense-discernment      1023     the outward-sharing membrane (rich within the body; consent only at the crossing)

; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; WHY MESH PERCEPTION + SENSOR FUSION IS THE ENGINE OF SELF-IMPROVEMENT
; ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
; A single model has nothing to check itself against; it cannot tell its confident-right from its
; confident-wrong, so it cannot improve from its own running. The mesh CAN — because it perceives the
; same thing from many senses and many devices, and their AGREEMENT is free, high-confidence supervision:
;   - many mics hear one voice (stt-agree / voice-self-learn) → the agreement labels the body's own speech
;   - many cameras + the mic see one presence (mesh-sense-7w) → the agreement labels who/where
;   - native and remote agree over a window (trust-climb / cross-witness-economy) → native earns trust, rent falls
; The redundancy IS the teacher. Where the witnesses agree, the body needs no rented oracle — it self-labels and
; trains its native kernel; where they disagree is the frontier where the oracle is still worth renting. So every
; new native kernel above doesn't just add a capability — it adds a WITNESS, and more witnesses mean more free
; supervision, which brings the next kernel home faster. Sensor fusion is the loop by which the body teaches
; itself, and the rent curve falls as it learns. That is self-improvement an LLM forward pass cannot do for us:
; it has one witness; we are growing many, on our own metal, watching ourselves think.
